Code and data for:

Lee PK, Zhou X, Hargreaves BA. Diffusion-prepared imaging with amplitude navigation for correction of motion-induced signal loss. Magn Reson Med. 2025;1-17. doi: 10.1002/mrm.30484

1. Create docker container using provided Dockerfile. Most convenient is to use VSCode with DevContainers extensions
2. Use jupytext to convert main.py to a notebook

>> jupytext --to ipynb main.py

3. Run the code and change the loaded data directory if desired

Data is available at 

Lee, P. K. (2024). k-space Dataset for No-Stabilizer Diffusion Prepared Sequence [Data set]. Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.13771055
